===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Gladion (Masters)}}
Gladion forms a [[sync pair]] with {{TP|Gladion|Silvally}}, {{p|Golbat}}, {{p|Magearna}}, {{p|Weavile}}, and {{p|Porygon-Z}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. His Silvally can change into an opponent's type weakness once per battle. Gladion became a playable sync pair on September 14, 2020.

Gladion first appeared as an NPC during the [[story event]] [[Family Ties]]. He has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]]. 

